        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A PC can rally an orphan with a successful Diplomacy check (DC 15; Intimidation does not work). A rallied orphan can use the Aid reaction to help a PC's attack or skill check, or reveal what it knows about the fishery and Gaedren. <strong>Story:</strong> rescuing the orphans is the heart of this dungeon (see the Treasure/XP notes); one orphan is the payoff for a PC with the 'Missing Child' background hook.</p>"
